2d array
______________

How to declare 2d array

datatype arrname[][];

int    arr[][];

How to create or instatntion  2d array
__________________________________________

datatype arrname[][];
arrname=new datatype[r][c];

or
datatype arrname[][]=new datatype[r][c];

r->collection of 1 darray 
c->each 1d array no of elements (every row same element  matrix format)


initlization
____________
arrname[rindex][cindex]=element;


